These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-1::.
4 different games are played: scrabble, canasta, bridge, poker
4 different pets are kept: rat, horse, rabbit, goat
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, ice-hockey, rugby, sailing
1. the owner of the goat is the person playing bridge##1
2. the person playing scrabble is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the rat is in an odd position##4
4. the owner of the rabbit is not the person playing scrabble##6
5. the person who's sport is rugby is not the owner of the goat##6
6. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the owner of the rat##3
7. the owner of the rat is somewhere between the person playing bridge and the owner of the horse##7
8. the person who's sport is badminton is between the person playing canasta and the person playing bridge##2
9. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Game   | bridge   | poker      | canasta   | scrabble  |
| Pet   | goat    | rabbit   | rat | horse  |
| Sport         | sailing | badminton | rugby     | ice-hockey |

