.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-2::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, skateboarding, cricket, biathlon
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, february, september, october
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, mexican, nigerian, polish
 1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person who's birthday is in august is in an odd position##4
 3. the person who's sport is cricket is not the person who's birthday is in february##6
 4. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person who's birthday is in september##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in august is the nigerian##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in september is the polish##1
 7. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the mexican##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the mexican##3
 9. the person who's sport is badminton is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in october and the person who's sport is cricket##7
10. the nigerian is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |     3     |   4    |
| Sport      | skateboarding | badminton         | cricket    | biathlon  |
| Birthday          | october     | february | august | september |
| Nationality   | colombian     | mexican     | nigerian  | polish |

