.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, camping, fishing, writing
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, cola, water, almond-milk
There are 4 different favourite colors: purple, emerald, ebony, light-blue
1. the person who likes ebony is somewhere to the right of the person who likes emerald##5
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is in an even position##4
3. the person who likes ebony is on the far right##1
4. the person drinking mirinda is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person who's hobby is fishing##2
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is not the person who likes light-blue##6
6. the person who's hobby is fishing is somewhere between the person who's hobby is camping and the person drinking cola##7
7. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
8. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
9. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the person who likes purple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |      4      |
| Hobby         | writing | fishing  | camping  | board-games |
| Beverage   | cola   | water | mirinda | almond-milk     |
| Color     | light-blue    | purple     | emerald     | ebony         |

