.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-4::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, gospel, jazz, salsa
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, western, animation, crime
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, photography, traveling, rock-climbing
1. the fan of jazz is on the far right##1
2. the person watching western movies is the person who's hobby is photography##1
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
4. the fan of gospel is the person who's hobby is photography##1
5. the person watching animation movies is the fan of salsa##1
6. the person watching epic movies is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
7. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
8. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere between the fan of gospel and the fan of jazz##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | gospel    | blues     | salsa   | jazz      |
| Movie-Genre   | western    | epic | animation | crime  |
| Hobby     | photography | hiking  | rock-climbing    | traveling |

