4. the argentine is somewhere between the person traveling to hannover and the american##7
5. the american is the owner of the rabbit##1
6. the german is on the far left or far right##3
7. the owner of the mouse is the german##1
8. the person traveling to edinburgh is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2   |    3     |    4     |
