The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, filmmaking, magic-tricks, photography
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bus, van, taxi
1. the person driving the taxi is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
2. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is chess##3
3. the person driving the van is somewhere to the right of the person who growsorchid##5
4. the person who growsmarigold is somewhere between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##7
5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person who growsorchid##1
6. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
7. the person who growsazalea is somewhere to the left of the person who growsbellflower##5
8. the person who growsmarigold is not the person driving the airplane##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |     3      |      4      |
| Flower      | azalea     | marigold | orchid        | bellflower       |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | chess    | filmmaking | photography |
| Transport   | taxi     | bus  | airplane    | van   |

