5. the person drinking milk is in an even position##4
6. the person who growsrose is somewhere to the left of the person who growssunflower##5
7. the musician is somewhere between the person drinking coffee and the person drinking soy-milk##7
8. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
