.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-8::.
There 4 different types of food: grapes, cranberry, cherry, artichoke
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, ritmeester, cain, bongani
4 different pets are kept: fish, hedgehog, lizard, rat
 1. the owner of the lizard is the person eating cranberry##1
 2. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
 3. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the left of the person eating artichoke##5
 4. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1
 5. the person eating grapes is on the far left##1
 6. the cain-smoker is somewhere to the left of the ritmeester-smoker##5
 7. the swisher-smoker is somewhere between the ritmeester-smoker and the bongani-smoker##7
 8. the person eating cherry is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 9. the swisher-smoker is somewhere to the right of the owner of the lizard##5
10. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person eating cherry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |    3    |     4     |
| Food         | grapes | cranberry      | cherry | artichoke |
| Cigar   | cain     | ritmeester | swisher  | bongani       |
| Pet           | rat         | lizard       | fish    | hedgehog  |

