5. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is rowing##5
6. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goldfish##5
7. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in october##5
8. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
9. the owner of the goat is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
