5. the person who likes blue is not the person who's birthday is in august##6
6. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the right of the owner of the fish##5
7. the owner of the rabbit is the person who likes grey##1
8. the person who likes turquise is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
9. the person who likes blue is somewhere between the owner of the fish and the person who's birthday is in february##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3      |   4    |
