 1. the coach is somewhere to the left of the gothic-revival house##5
 2. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 3. the craftsman house is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the art-deco house is between the freelancer and the journalist##2
 5. the wooden house is somewhere to the right of the engineer##5
 6. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the left of the person drinking milk##5
 7. the freelancer is not the person drinking fanta##6
 8. the wooden house is somewhere between the person drinking milk and the person drinking soy-milk##7
 9. the coach is somewhere to the left of the journalist##5
10. the craftsman house is on the left of the wooden house##1
11. the coach is between the journalist and the freelancer##2

.:: Answer ::.
